==French==
===Etymology===
Old French [[presse]] ‘closely’, from vulgar Latin ''*presso'', from Latin [[pressus]] ‘concise’, from [[premere]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/pʀɛ/}}

===Adverb===
'''près'''
# [[near]], [[close]]
#:''Mon anniversaire est très '''près'''.''  It's my birthday soon.
#:''J'habite tout '''près'''.''  I live just nearby.

===Derived terms===
*[[de près]]
*[[près de]]

